article_text:
Jeff Wheeler – Star Tribune

Gallery: Nicole Logan of Hancock, MN was hugged by a friend after she finished the walk on Sunday afternoon. It was her first time doing the walk; she's a cancer survivor, having been cancer free for a year.

og.description: Hundreds of Susan G. Komen Twin Cities 3-Day participants concluded their 60-mile journey raising more than $1.6 million for breast cancer research and community outreach programs.
